verse_part: and hast made me to reign
the top of each of them
of that on the right hand
and they carry them away captives
Then will I pluck them up by the roots
after the manner of the nations
or with them that have no
nor to him that came in,
and that he himself had dedicated,
that thou mayest carry me out
thou hast given us to inherit.
and when they had made an end
and when they had slain him,
he shall be put to death:
And it came to pass, as he talked
And when they had made an end
so that they shall come again
they had utterly destroyed them all.
